extu (x, 31 - msb, 32 - nbits)

clru (x, lsb, msb)

setu (x, lsb, msb)


where
  msb: position of the most significant bit of the changed field
  lsb: position of the least significant bit of the changed field
  nbits: no of bits in the change field

  position of the left most bit is 31, and the right most bit is 0.
